<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3149291" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U" oldref="6"><variable id="references_modify"><link href="text/swriter/guide/references_modify.xhp" name="Modifying Cross-References">Modifying Cross-References</link>
</variable></paragraph>
<list type="ordered">
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3153132" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="2">Click in front of the cross-reference that you want to modify.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3149632" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="3">If you cannot see the field shading of the cross-reference, choose <emph>View - Field Shadings</emph> or press <emph>Ctrl+F8</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3149611" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="4">Choose <emph>Edit - Fields</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3145101" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="7">Set the options that you want, and then click <emph>OK</emph>.</paragraph>
</listitem>
</list>
<paragraph role="tip" id="par_id3154255" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="5">Use the arrow buttons in the <emph>Edit Fields </emph>dialog to browse through the cross-references in the current document.</paragraph>
